org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject, LidarSystem, ObjectDetectionSensorSystem, ObjectTrackingSensorSystem, RoboticSystem, SensorSystem, System
public class LidarSystemImpl
extends ObjectDetectionSensorSystemImpl
implements LidarSystem

An implementation of the model object 'Lidar System'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Nb Layers
  • Layer Angle Min
  • Layer Angle Step
  • Noise
  • Sigma Noise
  • Angle min
  • Angle max
  • Time increment
  • Scan time
  • Range min
  • Range max
